title: 为什么Vehicles载具没有放置权限
author: g519403080
txt_content:
这是官方的全部权限

Bikes.openShop - Permission to open the shop
Bikes.giveBike - giveBike command permission
Bikes.getBike - getBike command permission
Bikes.overrideOwner - Use or remove another's bike
Bikes.overrideOwner.ride - Use another's bike
Bikes.bikeList - Bike List command
Bikes.overrideWorld - Use bikes in not allowed worlds
Bikes.overrideRemoveOnDismount - Bikes won't be removed and added back to your inventory on dismount if removeBikeOnDismount enabled.
